Audio files required before deployment:

- drone.mp3: Low ambient drone, approximately 40Hz fundamental, with Morse code embedded at 0.5% volume
  Morse message: HERAI IS NOT A PLACE
  Use Audacity to compose. Export at 192kbps.

- transmission_00.wav: Wind and static WAV file with DeepSound steganography payload embedded.
  See /private/SPOILERS.md for full payload text.
  Store the DeepSound project file in /private/deepsound-project/
